  ministry `Ministry of Personnel, Public Grievances and Pensions`
  department `Department of Personnel and Training`
  longTitle `An Act to make provision for the constitution of a special police force in Delhi for the investigation of certain offences in the Union territories for the superintendence and administration of the said force and for the extension to other areas 3* * * of the powers and jurisdiction of members of the said force in regard to the investigation of the said offences.`
